# .trivyignore — CVEs accepted in CERNIQ supply chain.
#
# Mirrors the OD-021 acceptance list in `osv-scanner.toml` because
# trivy reads its own ignore format, NOT the osv-scanner config. If
# you add an acceptance row to `osv-scanner.toml`, mirror it here.
#
# Each entry MUST cite its OD- decision row + a sunset condition.
# Acceptance is operator policy; do not add lines without an OD-XXX.

